TopicTitle: My Youtube Channel For My Video Projects

Articles.Content:
Hello! I just wanted to inform you guys that I've started a youtube channel. I intend to use it for sharing my video-editing projects, filmmaking attempts, and as a way of advertising the stories I write and share on my Wattpad account.

https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC_1oTgiDYDEt-PZwp_g8_nA

There are currently four videos, all are short snippets of footage, so far there are none over a minute in length, but my next project will challenge that.

Anyway, I figured that someone may be interested in whatever monstrosities I have wrought.

Some material may be KSP-related, by the way. We'll just have to wait and see.

Interesting!

I have to admit, a few of your videos are a bit random though.
